    • loadListOfTargetStates

      ArrayList<TFState> loadListOfTargetStates(int wDim, int numStates, String statesFile)
      Load a sequence of states from a file, and return the list
      Parameters:
      wDim - dimension of the world

    • testMakeSeqOfSteps

      public void testMakeSeqOfSteps(int wDim, int tX, int tY, int numSteps, String fileSteps, String fileStates) throws IOException, org.sat4j.specs.ContradictionException, org.sat4j.specs.TimeoutException
